{
  "stem": "18474.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- we were always fighting, the gentile kids and the Jewish kids, we-- we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a way of life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know any different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the public school, which is run by the-- by the government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In school, we used to speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the street, the majority of the people were Ukrainian, so you'd speak Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At home, you used to speak Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war broke out, I was--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1939, I was at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Seen the Russians march in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I-- it was a new-- a new era, a new-- the Polish people, you know, there was no more Poland and sort of, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's hard to tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know the regime, we didn't know the-- what's right before us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But nobody bothered us really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not right away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we could see it coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They tried-- the government was organized [INAUDIBLE] these collective farms, you know, and different things, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was starting to run by the government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Than the war came in '41 and everything was disrupted, everything was cut off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Make a living, he were working in a mill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a flour mill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He were hauling wheat and flour to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had a little business from coal, lime, which was run by my father and my mother and the kids.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was a very-- we used to sell the lime and the coal to the farmers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they used to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was a way of life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean when the Russians came?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still doing more or less the same thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't bother us yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
